data.description: For investors seeking an immediate tenant-in-place opportunity, your search ends here. The present property owners express their interest in leasing back the property for a period ranging from 1.5 to 2 years. Introducing Annabella's Townhomes, an exclusive community characterized by coziness and accessibility. Immerse yourself in a world of leisure, complete with a sparkling swimming pool, and the added luxury of professional grounds upkeep, guaranteeing you the ultimate relaxation. Prepare to be enchanted by this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom townhome, a genuine rarity within this community. It stands as the most spacious 3-bedroom offering, encompassing a generous 1713 square feet. Enter the heart of this home, where the kitchen takes center stage, showcasing its refined granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an inviting breakfast bar. The open floor plan seamlessly blends practicality and elegance, making it an ideal setting for hosting guests and crafting enduring memories. Revel in the convenience of the first-floor master suite, featuring its private ensuite bathroom, just a stone's throw from the welcoming living area. Upstairs, you'll uncover three bedrooms, each boasting its distinctive allure. Two of these bedrooms provide abundant space, while the master bedroom offers a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom. Furthermore, the unit includes a capacious two-car garage, ensuring ample room for your vehicles and storage requirements. Annabella's Townhomes invites you to savor a lifestyle that seamlessly combines low-maintenance living with an unbeatable location.
